        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-deep-navy mt-8 mb-4">5. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at 
          <a href="mailto:support@amplifly.ai" class="text-bright-blue hover:underline">support@amplifly.ai</a>.
        </p>
